{"tid":1147822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭博社：中美談判氣氛低落「幾乎沒有進展」","createTime":"2019-05-10T05:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T05:37:52.000Z","uid":41404,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"acd0a442fef8bdac25dbb4e898daa98d716b7147","tid":1147822,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T05:25:38.000Z","msg":"彭博社引述消息人士指，中美雙方談判氣氛低落，近乎沒有進展。中國商務部確認美方已將關稅升級，表示對此深表遺憾，將不得不採取必要反制措施。商務部指，希望雙方相向而行、共同努力，通過合作和協商辦法解決存在的問題。關稅實施後，美國股市有所下挫，惟亞太區波動不大，人民弊更稍見回升。<br />\n<br />\n劉鶴在談判前表示，希望在當前特殊形勢下，理性、坦誠地與美方交換意見。他又強調加徵關稅不是解決問題的辦法，認為不只對中美雙方不利，對全球也不利。他逗留了約90分鐘後離開。會談後，劉鶴和萊蒂澤以及姆紐欽在當地時間約8時40分共進晚餐。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190510/mobile/bkn-20190510004538808-0510_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190510%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190510004538808-0510_00822_001.html&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=21417634\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190510/mobile/bkn-20190510004538808-0510_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"add00f9a69ed4fdbc9e6a49eb1aac605b0e72042","tid":1147822,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T05:28:53.000Z","msg":"美國股市有所下挫，惟亞太區波動不大，人民弊更稍見回升。 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" clas